oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Nashville Celebrates Harold Bradley
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Bradley, Harold; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (black on white) announcing Harold Bradley, 8 decades of making music history, to be given the 2016 Cecil Scaife Visionary Award at the Musicians Hall of Fame and Museum in Nashville on May 17. Poster features a metal photoplate of Harold Bradley.
